      "created_at": "2023-08-01T08:50:02.632Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi Tom, something is wrong here.  You will see fluctuations (more in the \u00b115w range or even less) but if you are pedaling fairly consistently it should not be this big.  We have other users that have recently started seeing power dropouts which we believe is something we need to fix in our app and we are working on this now.</p>\n<p>The weird thing is we have a Flux S and no issues.  Can you go to activities on our website and send me a link to your workout and we can help evaluate the accuracy of the ramp test or tell you what it should be if it is wrong.</p>",
