      "cooked": "<p>Hi Alex,</p>\n<p>Thanks for getting back to me.</p>\n<p>I accidentally didn\u2019t save the workout so can\u2019t access it on my activities.</p>\n<p>I also did a Zwift ramp test a few days ago and had the same problem on that so quit early.</p>\n<p>Could this be a problem with the tacx that I need to contact garmin about?</p>\n<p>Thanks,<br>\nTom</p>",
