      "created_at": "2023-08-01T15:45:32.011Z",
      "cooked": "<p>It could be something like bluetooth interference from wifi or some other wireless product.   If you have an Android device that supports Ant+ (previous generations of Samsung for example) then you could try Ant+.  I would say you should be able to try any workout and see these issues, so you could try something easier than a ramp test.  If I can see workout link (ideally) or screenshot it would for sure help.  It is possible it is a device issue but that I would say is usually less likely.</p>",
